<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٦٩:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {كَلَّا بَلْ لَا تُكْرِمُونَ الْيَتِيمَ <span class="c2">(١٧)</span> وَلَا تَحَاضُّونَ عَلَى طَعَامِ الْمِسْكِينِ <span class="c2">(١٨)</span> وَتَأْكُلُونَ التُّرَاثَ أَكْلًا لَمًّا <span class="c2">(١٩)</span> وَتُحِبُّونَ الْمَالَ حُبًّا جَمًّا <span class="c2">(٢٠)</span>} <span class="c4">[الفجر: ١٧ - ٢٠]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{تَحَاضُّونَ}</span>: <span class="c2">«تُحَافِظُونَ»</span>،<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(تَحُضُّونَ)</span>: <span class="c2">«تَأْمُرُونَ بِإِطْعَامِهِ»</span>،<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> <span class="c3">{أَكْلًا لَمًّا}</span>: <span class="c2">«السَّفُّ»</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c3">{جَمًّا}</span>: <span class="c2">«الكَثِيرُ»</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>